WEBVTT

00:05.579 --> 00:09.897
Life Paint is a unique spray, different to other reflective products on the market.

00:11.979 --> 00:15.485
When you apply it to a surface, the reflective particles would stick together...

00:15.558 --> 00:19.377
...with a special adhesive, making the spray invisible by day,...

00:21.629 --> 00:23.985
...but light up at night in the glare of headlights.

00:24.613 --> 00:29.243
I think cycle safety in London is not all about bicycles, it's about cars,...

00:29.343 --> 00:32.102
...it's about pedestrians, it's about sharing the road with other users,...

00:32.212 --> 00:34.441
...so it's great that the car brand has got involved...

00:34.957 --> 00:38.474
...to essentially help cyclists and help drivers in the end and save lives.

